                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for producing BDO and co-producing other alcohols from maleic anhydride",
                    "一种顺酐生产BDO并联产其他醇类物的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for producing BDO and co-producing other alcohols from maleic anhydride, and belongs to the technical field of chemical engineering. The method comprises the following steps: carrying out hydrolysis reaction on maleic anhydride and water to obtain a maleic acid reactant; the method comprises the following steps: carrying out esterification reaction on a maleic acid reactant and olefin to obtain an alkyl maleate product containing dialkyl maleate, monoalkyl maleate, residual maleic acid and residual maleic anhydride; carrying out hydrogenation reaction on a dialkyl maleate product obtained by separating the alkyl maleate product and hydrogen to obtain a hydrogenation product containing BDO and other alcohols; and separating the hydrogenation product to obtain a BDO product and other alcohol products. The invention provides a technical route with low production cost and high atom economy for producing BDO and co-producing other alcohols at the same time. The esterification reaction and the hydrogenation reaction have very high selectivity and conversion rate, the atom utilization rate is 100%, and the energy consumption is low. The method has the advantages of low material loss, low unit product energy consumption and the like."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种顺酐生产BDO并联产其他醇类物的方法，属于化工技术领域。该方法包括：将顺酐与水进行水解反应，得到马来酸待反应物；将马来酸待反应物与烯烃进行酯化反应，得到包含马来酸二烷基酯、马来酸单烷基酯、剩余马来酸和剩余顺酐的马来酸烷基酯产物；将马来酸烷基酯产物分离得到的马来酸二烷基酯产品与氢气进行加氢反应，得到包含BDO和其他醇类物的加氢产物；将加氢产物分离得到BDO产品和其他醇类产品。本发明为生产BDO同时联产其他醇类提供了一条生产成本低、原子经济性高的技术路线。本发明的酯化反应和加氢反应均具有很高的选择性和转化率，原子利用率100％，能耗低。本发明具有物料损耗低、单位产品能耗低等优点。"
                }
            ]
